  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we conducted experiments with two punctuators.",
    "First, we utilized the punctuations generated from the LLM ASR refinement process described in Section 3.2.",
    "Second, we employed a DeltaLM-based punctuation model, which was utilized in our previous year's submission (Liu et al., 2023).",
    "We observed that while the punctuations generated by the LLM were semantically correct, they often resulted in long sequences and led to a degradation in MT performance.",
    "As a result, we decided to opt for the second choice and segment the text into sentences using manually crafted rules."
  ],
